
/*
Database Technologies – Assignment 8
Use sub-query to solve following problems.
Note: To solve below queries, use “sales” database

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Write a query that uses a subquery to obtain all orders for the
customer named Cisneros. Assume you do not know his customer 
number (cnum).
*/
mysql> SELECT * FROM orders WHERE snum=
    -> (SELECT snum FROM customers WHERE cname ='Cisneros');
